data.description: Pine Island Ridge... Located one one of the highest natural elevations on Pine Island. 3 bed 1 bath, Cement/Block/Stucco home with un-attached garage/shop and fenced yard. Corner lot with side alley access to garage. Original terrazzo floor, Galley kitchen with access to back patio and yard. Take a look at this cozy home today.
